---
title: Gouda, Prosciutto & Fig Jam Sandwiches with Tomato & Arugula
description: The only thing better than a really great sandwich is one that takes just minutes to prepare! All you have to do is quickly assemble and dig right into this Really Great Sandwich, which features sweet fig jam, savory-salty prosciutto, and mild, nutty gouda packed into a crusty ciabatta bun. Juicy tomato and peppery arugula provide a fresh complement. If you’re working from home, put it together just before lunch; or whip it up in the morning before heading to the office. When your stomach starts to rumble, you’ll be gazing at that brown bag with heart eyes.
